        <type><ref refid="types_8h_1a312c7e8848187d110315ab83a7b3d4d0" kindref="member">int64_t</ref>(*</type>
        <definition>typedef int64_t(* ktrap_handler_t) (ktrapframe_t *ktf_ptr)</definition>
        <argsstring>)(ktrapframe_t *ktf_ptr)</argsstring>
        <name>ktrap_handler_t</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para><computeroutput>ktrap_handler_t</computeroutput>是异常/中断处理函数的函数类型, 函数原型为: <computeroutput>int64_t funcname(struct ktrapframe_t*)</computeroutput> </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>ktf_ptr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>指向被打断的程序的陷入帧, 程序的陷入帧将在<computeroutput>ktrap_enter</computeroutput>中构建在<computeroutput>S模式</computeroutput>的栈中</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>如果被打断的程序想要传参给异常/中断处理函数, 那么必须要通过寄存器来实现, 而所有的通用寄存器在<computeroutput>ktrap_enter</computeroutput>函数中会被保存到陷入帧中. 所以异常/中断处理函数必然可以通过陷入栈来获得被打断的程序传入的参数</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>RISC-V通过<computeroutput>a0~a7</computeroutput>寄存器传参, 因此在<computeroutput>ktrap_enter</computeroutput>中要把<computeroutput>ktrapframe</computeroutput>的地址保存到<computeroutput>a0</computeroutput>寄存器中 </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
